  <body id="DLM350823" prov-type="section">
    <prov id="DLM350824" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
      <heading>Title</heading>
      <prov.body>
        <subprov skeleton="no">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
          <para>
            <text>This Act is the Prisoners’ and Victims’ Claims Act 2005.</text>
          </para>
        </subprov>
      </prov.body>
    </prov>
    <prov id="DLM350825" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
      <heading>Commencement</heading>
      <prov.body>
        <subprov skeleton="no">
          <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
          <para>
            <text>This Act comes into force on the day after the date on which it receives the Royal assent.</text>
          </para>
        </subprov>
      </prov.body>
    </prov>
    <part id="DLM350826" in.amend="false" irdnumbering="no" toc="yes" date.first.valid="2005-06-04" act.no="74" act.type="public" date.as.at="2009-07-01" date.assent="2005-06-03" stage="reprint" year="2005">
      <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
      <heading>General provisions</heading>
      <prov id="DLM350827" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
        <heading>Purpose of this Act</heading>
        <prov.body>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
            <para>
              <text>The purpose of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304500" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="subpart 1 Compensation sought by claims by prisoners, etc" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749172" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>subpart 1</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309488" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749172" atidlm:targetKey="2109609" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351424" atidlm:targetName="subpart 1 Compensation sought by claims by prisoners, etc" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749172" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351424.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of Part 2</citation> is to restrict and guide the awarding of compensation sought by specified claims in order to help to ensure that the remedy of compensation is reserved for exceptional cases and used only if, and only to the extent that, it is necessary to provide effective redress.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <para>
              <text>The purpose of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1641603" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1900800 - subpart 2 Victims’ claims" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1906708" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>subpart 2</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="900243" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1906708" atidlm:targetKey="2110858" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351434" atidlm:targetName="subpart 2 Victims’ claims" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1906708" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of Part 2</citation> is to—</text>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                <para>
                  <text>establish, require payments into, and regulate the operation of, a victims’ claims trust bank account; and</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                <para>
                  <text>provide a procedure for the making and determination of victims’ claims.</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
            <para>
              <text>The purpose of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304502" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="subpart 3 Suspension of limitation periods for certain claims by victims" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749174" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>subpart 3</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309490" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749174" atidlm:targetKey="2111403" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351701" atidlm:targetName="subpart 3 Suspension of limitation periods for certain claims by victims" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749174" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351701.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of Part 2</citation> is to suspend the running of limitation periods for certain claims by victims.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">4</label>
            <para>
              <text>The purpose of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304503" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="part 3 Amendments to other Acts" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749175" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Part 3</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309491" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749175" atidlm:targetKey="2111803" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351705" atidlm:targetName="part 3 Amendments to other Acts" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749175" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351705.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> (amendments to other Acts) is to—</text>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                <para>
                  <text>amend the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304504" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Legal Services Act 2000" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749176" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Legal Services Act 2000</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309492" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749176" atidlm:targetKey="370200" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM71806" atidlm:targetName="Legal Services Act 2000" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749176" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM71806.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> to facilitate the granting of legal aid in respect of victims’ claims proceedings under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304505" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="subpart 2 Victims' claims" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749177" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>subpart 2</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309493" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749177" atidlm:targetKey="2110858" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351434" atidlm:targetName="subpart 2 Victims' claims" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749177" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of Part 2 of this Act</citation>; and</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                <para>
                  <text>amend the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304506" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Privacy Act 1993" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749178" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Privacy Act 1993</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309494" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749178" atidlm:targetKey="1539005" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM296638" atidlm:targetName="Privacy Act 1993" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749178" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM296638.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> to enable the Ministry of Justice to have access to Police records on offender identity and victim identity for the purpose of providing assistance to victims in accordance with this Act; and</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                <para>
                  <text>amend the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304507" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Victims' Rights Act 2002" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749179" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Victims’ Rights Act 2002</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309495" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749179" atidlm:targetKey="879006" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM157812" atidlm:targetName="Victims' Rights Act 2002" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749179" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM157812.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> to require the Secretary for Justice to request, for the purposes of a notice under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304508" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 20" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749180" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 20</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309496" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749180" atidlm:targetKey="2110814" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351447" atidlm:targetName="prov 20" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749180" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of this Act</citation>, the current address (including the full name) of a victim who has asked for notice of certain matters under that Act; and</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">d</label>
                <para>
                  <text>amend consequentially the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304509" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Human Rights Act 1993" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749181" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Human Rights Act 1993</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309497" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749181" atidlm:targetKey="1573056" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM304211" atidlm:targetName="Human Rights Act 1993" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749181" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM304211.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>, the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304510" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Limitation Act 1950" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749182" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Limitation Act 1950</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309498" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749182" atidlm:targetKey="1787832" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM262436" atidlm:targetName="Limitation Act 1950" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749182" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM262436.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>, and the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304511" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Privacy Act 1993" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749183" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Privacy Act 1993</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309499" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749183" atidlm:targetKey="1539005" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM296638" atidlm:targetName="Privacy Act 1993" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749183" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM296638.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350827" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>.</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
      </prov>
      <prov id="DLM350828" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">4</label>
        <heading>Interpretation</heading>
        <prov.body>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="no"/>
            <para>
              <text>In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,—</text>
              <def-para id="DLM350829">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350830">account</def-term> means the victims’ claims trust bank account established under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304512" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 54" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749184" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 54</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309500" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749184" atidlm:targetKey="2110848" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351491" atidlm:targetName="prov 54" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749184" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350829" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350831">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350832">accused</def-term>, in relation to any person who is alleged to be the victim of an offence, means a person charged (whether as a principal or party or an accessory after the fact or otherwise) with the commission of that offence</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350833">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350834">action</def-term> means any proceeding in a court or tribunal other than a criminal proceeding</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350835">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350836">child</def-term> means a boy or girl under the age of 14 years</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350837">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350838">civil custody</def-term> has the same meaning as in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304513" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 2" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749185" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 2(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309501" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749185" atidlm:targetKey="2572244" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401069" atidlm:targetName="prov 2" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749185" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350837" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971 </citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350839">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350840">community-based sentence</def-term> means—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a community-based sentence as defined in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304515" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 4" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749187" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 4(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309503" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749187" atidlm:targetKey="759803" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM135350" atidlm:targetName="prov 4" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749187" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM135347.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350839" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Sentencing Act 2002</citation>; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a community-based sentence as defined in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304517" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 2" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749189" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 2(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309505" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749189" atidlm:targetKey="442206" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM76621" atidlm:targetName="prov 2" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749189" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM76615.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350839" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Criminal Justice Act 1985</citation>; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a sentence of a similar kind to those referred to in paragraphs (a) and (b) (including, without limitation, a sentence of community care, a sentence of probation, or a sentence of residential periodic detention) imposed under an earlier corresponding enactment</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350841">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350842">compensation</def-term>—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>means any form of monetary compensation or damages (however described) required by a court or tribunal to be paid (including, without limitation, an amount of, or in the nature of, exemplary damages); and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>for the purposes only of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304521" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="subpart 2 Victims' claims" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749193" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>subpart 2</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309509" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749193" atidlm:targetKey="2110858" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351434" atidlm:targetName="subpart 2 Victims' claims" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749193" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350841" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of Part 2</citation>, includes any form of monetary compensation or damages (however described) required to be paid as, or as part of, an out-of-court final settlement of a claim (including, without limitation, an amount paid in final settlement of a claim for an amount of, or in the nature of, exemplary damages); and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>includes an amount or award of interest related to compensation or damages in paragraph (a) or (b); but</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">d</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>does not include an amount required or agreed to be paid as, or towards, the costs of making a claim</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM2194809" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                  <text><def-term id="DLM2194810" xml:lang="en-NZ">Court Martial</def-term> means the Court Martial of New Zealand established under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1986627" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM2194811 - prov 8" atidlm:xmlId="DLM2194844" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 8</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="1007827" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM2194844" atidlm:targetKey="10140002" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM1001934" atidlm:targetName="prov 8" atidlm:sourceName="DLM2194844" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM1001932.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM2194809" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Court Martial Act 2007</citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350843">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350844">detention quarter</def-term> means a building or part of a building set aside under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304524" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749196" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309512" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749196" atidlm:targetKey="2572255" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401062" atidlm:targetName="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749196" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350843" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> as a detention quarter</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350845">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350846">fine</def-term> includes—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a sum of money adjudged or ordered to be paid by a conviction or order, whether described as a fine or as costs, expenses, fees, or otherwise:</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>any costs, expenses, or fees payable in respect of the enforcement of any fine as defined in paragraph (a)</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350849">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350850">immediate family</def-term>, in relation to a victim,—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>means a member of the victim’s family, whānau, or other culturally recognised family group, who is in a close relationship with the victim at the time of the offence; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>to avoid doubt, includes a person who is—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>the victim’s spouse, civil union partner, or de facto partner; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>the victim’s child or a child of a person who is, or was, the victim’s spouse, civil union partner, or de facto partner; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">iii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>the victim’s brother or sister or the child of a person who is, or was, the spouse, civil union partner, or de facto partner of a parent of the victim; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">iv</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>a parent of the victim or a person who is, or was, the spouse, civil union partner, or de facto partner of a parent of the victim; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">v</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>a grandparent of the victim</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350851">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350852">incapable</def-term>, in relation to a person,—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>means that the person—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>lacks, wholly or partly, the capacity to understand the nature, and to foresee the consequences, of decisions in respect of matters relating to his or her personal care and welfare; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>has the capacity to understand the nature, and to foresee the consequences, of decisions in respect of matters relating to his or her personal care and welfare, but wholly lacks the capacity to communicate decisions in respect of matters of that kind; and</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>includes the person being in a state of continuing unconsciousness</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350853">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350854">Judge Advocate General</def-term> means the Judge Advocate General of the Armed Forces appointed under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304530" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 203" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749702" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 203</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309518" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749702" atidlm:targetKey="2587448" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM404209" atidlm:targetName="prov 203" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749702" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM404087.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350853" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350855">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350856">judgment</def-term> includes an award, direction, order, or other requirement</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350857">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350858">offence</def-term>, in relation to a victim, means an offence against an enactment—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>committed against the victim (or committed against a child or young person of whom the victim is a parent or legal guardian); or</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>through which, or by means of which, the victim (or a child or young person of whom the victim is a parent or legal guardian) suffered physical injury or emotional harm, or loss of, or damage to, property; or</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>that resulted in the death of a member of the victim’s immediate family, or in a member of the victim’s immediate family being incapable</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350859">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350860">offender</def-term> has the meaning given to it by <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304532" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 5" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749704" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 5</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309681" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749704" atidlm:targetKey="2108657" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351401" atidlm:targetName="prov 5" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749704" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350859" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350861">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350862">penal institution</def-term> has the same meaning as in section 2(1) of the Penal Institutions Act 1954</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350863">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350864">parent</def-term> has the same meaning as in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304533" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 2" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749705" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 2(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309682" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749705" atidlm:targetKey="838745" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM147094" atidlm:targetName="prov 2" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749705" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM147087.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350863" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Children, Young Persons, and Their Families Act 1989</citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350865">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350866">person arrested and detained under the Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971 pending release or trial</def-term> means a person who, in accordance with that Act, and in or outside New Zealand, is—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>arrested for an alleged offence, and detained before being delivered into civil custody, service custody, or other custody, in connection with the offence; or</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>in any of those kinds of custody pending release, or pending trial for the alleged offence by a court of competent jurisdiction in or outside New Zealand</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM1037302">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM1037303">person under control or supervision</def-term> means—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a prisoner:</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person who is subject to a community-based sentence:</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person who is subject to a sentence of home detention imposed under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="627412" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1037304 - prov 80A" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1037317" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 80A</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="547612" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1037317" atidlm:targetKey="765001" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM136401" atidlm:targetName="prov 80A" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1037317" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM136400.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Sentencing Act 2002</citation>:</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">d</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person who is serving a sentence of imprisonment on home detention as defined in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="627413" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1037305 - prov 4" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1037318" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 4(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="547613" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1037318" atidlm:targetKey="759803" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM135350" atidlm:targetName="prov 4" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1037318" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM135347.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Sentencing Act 2002</citation> (prior to the commencement of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="627414" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1037307 - prov 72" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1037319" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 72</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="547614" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1037319" atidlm:targetKey="2567627" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM411451" atidlm:targetName="prov 72" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1037319" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM411030.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Parole Amendment Act 2007</citation>); but also includes home detention as defined in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="627415" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1037308 - prov 2" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1037320" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 2(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="547615" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1037320" atidlm:targetKey="442206" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM76621" atidlm:targetName="prov 2" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1037320" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM76615.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Criminal Justice Act 1985</citation>:</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">e</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person who is subject to conditions—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1641604" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1900801 - Parole Act 2002" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1906709" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Parole Act 2002</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="900244" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1906709" atidlm:targetKey="775400" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM137631" atidlm:targetName="Parole Act 2002" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1906709" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM137631.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> (including, without limitation, conditions applying to a person who is subject to an extended supervision order under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="627416" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1037309 - prov 107I" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1037321" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 107I</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="547616" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1037321" atidlm:targetKey="783629" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM139630" atidlm:targetName="prov 107I" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1037321" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM139601.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of that Act</citation>); or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="627417" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1037306 - prov 80N" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1037322" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 80N</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="547617" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1037322" atidlm:targetKey="765014" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM136414" atidlm:targetName="prov 80N" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1037322" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM136400.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> or <atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="653601" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1055800 - prov 93" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1055801" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>93</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="553881" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1055801" atidlm:targetKey="767428" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM136469" atidlm:targetName="prov 93" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1055801" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM136441.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Sentencing Act 2002</citation>; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">iii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>of a similar kind under earlier corresponding enactments:</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">f</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person who is arrested and detained under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1641605" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM1900802 - Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:xmlId="DLM1906710" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="900245" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM1906710" atidlm:targetKey="2572255" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401062" atidlm:targetName="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:sourceName="DLM1906710" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM1037302" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> pending release or trial:</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">g</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a service detainee or a service prisoner</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350869">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350870">prison</def-term> has the same meaning as in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304540" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 3" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749712" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 3(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309689" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749712" atidlm:targetKey="1698014" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM294857" atidlm:targetName="prov 3" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749712" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM294853.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350869" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Corrections Act 2004</citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350871">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350872">prisoner</def-term> means—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person (in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304542" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 7" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749714" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 7</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309691" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749714" atidlm:targetKey="2108627" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351412" atidlm:targetName="prov 7" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749714" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350871" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> called a <def-term id="DLM350873">2004 Act prisoner</def-term>) who is not a service detainee or a service prisoner but who is for the time being in the legal custody under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304543" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Corrections Act 2004" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749715" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Corrections Act 2004</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309692" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749715" atidlm:targetKey="1696206" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM294848" atidlm:targetName="Corrections Act 2004" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749715" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM294848.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350871" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> of either of the following persons:</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>the chief executive (as defined in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304544" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 3" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749716" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 3(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309693" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749716" atidlm:targetKey="1698014" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM294857" atidlm:targetName="prov 3" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749716" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM294853.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350871" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of that Act</citation>):</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>the Commissioner of Police; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a person (in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304545" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 7" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749717" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 7</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309694" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749717" atidlm:targetKey="2108627" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351412" atidlm:targetName="prov 7" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749717" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350871" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> called a <def-term id="DLM350874">1954 Act prisoner</def-term>) who is not a service detainee or a service prisoner but who is for the time being in the legal custody of the Superintendent of a penal institution</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350875">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350876">Secretary</def-term> means the Secretary for Justice; and includes a person or body authorised by the Secretary to exercise or perform his or her functions, powers, and duties under this Act</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350877">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350878">Secretary of the Tribunal</def-term> means the officer or employee of the Ministry of Justice who is for the time being exercising or performing the functions, powers, or duties of that office</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350879">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350880">sentence of imprisonment</def-term>—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>means a sentence of imprisonment imposed before or after the commencement of this Act and under any 1 or more enactments or other rules of law (for example, under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304546" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749718" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309695" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749718" atidlm:targetKey="2572255" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401062" atidlm:targetName="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749718" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350879" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> or the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304547" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Sentencing Act 2002" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749719" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Sentencing Act 2002</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309696" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749719" atidlm:targetKey="758400" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM135341" atidlm:targetName="Sentencing Act 2002" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749719" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM135341.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350879" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>); and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>includes the following (as defined in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304548" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 4" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749720" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 4(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309697" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749720" atidlm:targetKey="759803" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM135350" atidlm:targetName="prov 4" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749720" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM135347.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350879" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Sentencing Act 2002</citation>):</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>a determinate sentence of imprisonment; and</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>an indeterminate sentence of imprisonment; but</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">c</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>does not include a term of imprisonment imposed, whether by committal, sentence, or order, for—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>non-payment of a sum of money; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>disobedience of a court order; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">iii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>contempt of court</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350881">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350882">service detainee</def-term> means a person who is—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                      <text>undergoing a sentence, imposed under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1986628" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM2194800 - Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:xmlId="DLM2194845" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="1007828" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM2194845" atidlm:targetKey="2572255" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401062" atidlm:targetName="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:sourceName="DLM2194845" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350881" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> by the Court Martial or a disciplinary officer, that includes the punishment of detention; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>in accordance with that Act, for the time being in or outside New Zealand—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>in civil custody or service custody while awaiting delivery to the prison, penal institution, or service penal establishment in which he or she is to serve his or her sentence; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>serving the term of his or her detention in a detention quarter, in service custody, or as field punishment</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350883">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350884">service penal establishment</def-term> has the same meaning as in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304551" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 2" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749723" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 2(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309700" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749723" atidlm:targetKey="2572244" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401069" atidlm:targetName="prov 2" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749723" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350883" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350885">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350886">service prison</def-term> has the same meaning as in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304553" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 2" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749725" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 2(1)</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309702" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749725" atidlm:targetKey="2572244" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401069" atidlm:targetName="prov 2" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749725" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350885" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of the Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350887">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350888">service prisoner</def-term> means a person who is—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>undergoing a sentence, imposed under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304555" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749727" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="leg-title" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309704" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749727" atidlm:targetKey="2572255" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401062" atidlm:targetName="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749727" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350887" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> by <insertwords>the Court Martial</insertwords>, that includes imprisonment; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>in accordance with that Act, for the time being in or outside New Zealand—</text>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>in civil custody or service custody while awaiting delivery to the prison, penal institution, or service penal establishment in which he or she is to serve his or her sentence; or</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                      <label-para skeleton="no">
                        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                        <para>
                          <text>serving the sentence of imprisonment in a prison, penal institution, service prison, detention quarter, or in other service custody</text>
                        </para>
                      </label-para>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350889">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350890">specified claim</def-term> has the meaning given to it by <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304556" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 6" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749728" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 6</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309705" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749728" atidlm:targetKey="2108620" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351403" atidlm:targetName="prov 6" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749728" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350889" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350891">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350892">specified internal and external complaints mechanisms</def-term> has the meaning given to it by <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304557" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 7" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749729" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 7</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309706" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749729" atidlm:targetKey="2108627" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351412" atidlm:targetName="prov 7" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749729" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350891" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350893">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350894">Tribunal</def-term>—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>means a Victims’ Special Claims Tribunal referred to in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304558" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 58" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749730" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 58</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309707" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749730" atidlm:targetKey="2110853" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351496" atidlm:targetName="prov 58" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749730" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350893" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>in relation to a victim’s claim filed under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304559" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 28" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749731" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 28</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309708" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749731" atidlm:targetKey="2110824" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351457" atidlm:targetName="prov 28" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749731" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350893" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>, means the particular Victims’ Special Claims Tribunal to which the claim has been referred under <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304560" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 30" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749732" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 30</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309709" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749732" atidlm:targetKey="2110827" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351459" atidlm:targetName="prov 30" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749732" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351434.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350893" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350895">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350896">victim</def-term> has the meaning given to it in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304561" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 8" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749733" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 8</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309710" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749733" atidlm:targetKey="2108629" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351419" atidlm:targetName="prov 8" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749733" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350895" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350897">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM350898">victim’s claim</def-term> has the meaning given to it in <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304562" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="prov 9" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749734" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>section 9</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309711" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749734" atidlm:targetKey="2108630" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351421" atidlm:targetName="prov 9" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749734" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM350897" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation></text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
              <def-para id="DLM350899">
                <para>
                  <text><def-term id="DLM351400">young person</def-term> means a boy or girl of or over the age of 14 years but under 17 years; but does not include a person who is or has been married or in a civil union.</text>
                </para>
              </def-para>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
