      <prov id="DLM351401" irdnumbering="no" skeleton="no" toc="yes">
        <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">5</label>
        <heading>Offender</heading>
        <prov.body>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">1</label>
            <para>
              <text>In this Act, <def-term id="DLM351402">offender</def-term>, in relation to a victim, means—</text>
              <label-para skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">a</label>
                <para>
                  <text>for the purposes only of <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="304563" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="subpart 3 Suspension of limitation periods for certain claims by victims" atidlm:xmlId="DLM749735" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>subpart 3</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="intref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="309712" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM749735" atidlm:targetKey="2111403" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM351701" atidlm:targetName="subpart 3 Suspension of limitation periods for certain claims by victims" atidlm:sourceName="DLM749735" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/Doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM351701.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM351401" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link> of Part 2</citation>, a person—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>convicted (alone or with others) by a court or <insertwords>the Court Martial</insertwords> of the offence that affected the victim; and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>on whom a court or <insertwords>the Court Martial</insertwords> has, because of the person’s conviction for that offence, imposed a sentence of imprisonment (the <def-term id="DLM1906700">sentence of imprisonment for the offence</def-term>); and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </label-para>
              <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">b</label>
                <para xml:lang="en-NZ">
                  <text>for all other purposes, a person found guilty (alone or with others) by a court or <insertwords>the Court Martial</insertwords> of the offence that affected the victim, or found guilty of that offence (alone or with others) by a disciplinary officer under the <citation jurisdiction="nz"><atidlm:link xmlns:atidlm="http://www.arbortext.com/namespace/atidlm" atidlm:key="1986632" atidlm:branchLabel="_NOVERSION_" atidlm:name="DLM2194802 - Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:xmlId="DLM2194849" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:linkcontent>Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971</atidlm:linkcontent><atidlm:resourcepair atidlm:markupType="extref" atidlm:isIncludeOrRef="1" atidlm:seqNum="1007832" atidlm:sourceXmlId="DLM2194849" atidlm:targetKey="2572255" atidlm:targetXmlId="DLM401062" atidlm:targetName="Armed Forces Discipline Act 1971" atidlm:sourceName="DLM2194849" atidlm:targetLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM401062.xml" atidlm:sourceLocator="file:///C:/epicuser/doctypes/NZAct/fragxyxz_DLM350826.xml" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"><atidlm:metadata atidlm:name="Parent_id" atidlm:value="DLM351401" atidlm:locale="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation>, or who pleads guilty to that offence (alone or with others) before a court or <insertwords>the Court Martial</insertwords> or a disciplinary officer.</text>
                </para>
              </label-para>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">2</label>
            <para>
              <text>For the purposes of subsection (1)(a), it does not matter whether, at the time the court or <insertwords>the Court Martial</insertwords> imposed the sentence of imprisonment for the offence, the person was already subject to, or was at that time or later also made subject to, a sentence of imprisonment for another offence or offences.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
        <notes>
